        <p>GCSE and IGCSE are internationally recognised qualifications highly desirable and highly valued by both the education institutions and employers.</p>
        <br/><p>IGCSEs are the same qualification level as a standard GCSE and can offer progression to A-Level,

BTEC vocational courses, and other similar qualifications that are recognised internationally and by

